songs.title: Friends Don’t Lie (Snippet)
songs.lyrics:
Lyrics from Snippet:

[Verse: Andy Mineo]
Don't–lie to me!
Gimme that–ugly truth over pretty lies
That faithful girl over pretty thighs
What a lucky guy, I don't gotta choose
She got an attitude-y? Ha, absolutely
Keep it honey-proof like the apps [?]
She b-b-b-bad and boujee!
Got a bigger booty than that lil' rapper Uzi
(I'm straight)
